    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1921-08-10T06:24:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1921-08-10T06:24:00-05:00" n="783"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d783">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.48/1512: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Commissioner at Riga</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Young</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Riga</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-08-10T13:00:00+01:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 10, 1921—1 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 7 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>477. Brown and party arrived this morning. Litvinov<note n="24" xml:id="d783fn24"
                        >Assistant Soviet Commissar of Foreign Affairs.</note> charged with
                    conducting negotiations with Brown on behalf of Russian famine committee also
                    arrived this morning. The six Americans named in my telegram number 476, August
                    8, 5 p.m.,<note n="25" xml:id="d783fn25">Not printed; see telegram, Aug. 10, 1
                        p.m., from the Consul at Reval, <ref target="#pg_801">p. 801</ref>.</note>
                    arrived Narva last night and are expected at Reval this morning. First meeting
                    Brown and Litvinov will probably take place this afternoon. Brown will limit
                    discussion to release other Americans and will ascertain whether Litvinov is
                    authorized to negotiate on behalf of Soviet authorities.</p>
                <p>Our number 475 omitted.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Young</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
